de_sugarcane is a port with remake of the de_sugarcane from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

- Complete the task: A bomb defusal map, installed in the on the indicated terrain.

- The minimap is attached.

// Official map by Valve. This map is used in Official Matchmaking in CS:GO. It can be played in Deathmatch and Demolition.
